The evidence with the title 'Rand Paul: U.S. borrows $1 million a minute | politifact ' says Jul 21, 2015  ... Rand Paul , R-Ky., talked about one of his favorite dislikes: the national debt.  ... Does anybody here think it 's a good idea to borrow money from China to send it to Pakistan ? We borrow a million dollars every minute.  ... Borrowing $ 1 million a minute would mean the government borrows $ 525 billion a year. 
